Welcu Api V1
============

Ruby Wrapper for the Welcu API V1 (http://developer.welcu.com/v1/)

Installation
============

Use

  gem install welcu

and

  require 'welcu_api'

or using Bundler, in your Gemfile:

  gem 'welcu', :require => 'welcu_api'

